  "general_provisions": "This bill addresses expungement of criminal records.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This bill:<hr><ltbullet>modifies a term related to the expungement of criminal records;<hr><ltbullet>addresses eligibility for expungement when there is a criminal protective order, a criminal stalking injunction, or a civil protective order; and<hr><ltbullet>addresses the numerical limits that make a petitioner ineligible to receive a certificate of eligibility for an expungement.",
